because you find it ugly.

23
00:00:49,597 --> 00:00:53,617
But wait just... hours

24
00:00:53,614 --> 00:00:56,844
and see how it will be developed to a great article.

25
00:00:56,842 --> 00:00:59,392
The "edit" button: click it, and change something,

26
